en_752735_0	As part of its ongoing Corporate Social Responsibility (CSR) projects, 573 Brigade troops under the 57 Division of the Security Force Headquarters - Kilinochchi launched a self-help (Shramadana) programme to clean Uriyan pre-school premises on Thursday (2).
en_752735_1	Commanding Officer, 1 Sri Lanka Sinha Regiment (SLSR) of the 573 Brigade carried out the project with his troops and a group of villagers in the area.
en_752735_2	Under the guidance of Major General Pradeep de Silva, General Officer Commanding, 57 Division and also under the supervision of the Commander 573 Brigade, organized the project as a community-oriented gesture.
